title: NYC MISC
description: Aaaaaand they're back! Coming off the excitement and feedback of episode 1, the Gals answering all of your questions about NYC living. Sprinkling in a few fun facts, Charlotte & Leanne return to the mic to share their dreams of being promoters and becoming actual adults that flip their mattresses.
